I've read so many histories of Israel/Palestine, who lived where when, who was a country and who wasn't, who got pushed off first, etc. etc. there are as many differences of opinion as there are books about it... but it's all pointless.  We need to stop living in the past, and look at this situation for what it is -- a lot of people living in an area who need to figure out a way to live together, prosper and get along.<br>
<br>
